Package: afflib
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: afflib is library for support of the Advanced Forensic Format (AFF).
 afflib is library for support of the Advanced Forensic Format (AFF).
 AFF(R) is an open and extensible file format designed to store disk images and
 associated metadata.

Package: afflib-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: afflib (= ${Source-Version})
Description: Header files and libraries for developing applications for afflib
 Header files and libraries for developing applications for afflib

Package: afflib-tools
Section: utils
Architecture: any
Depends: afflib (= ${Source-Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Several tools for reading and writing AFF files
 Several tools for reading and writing AFF files.

